08-09 May - Pasta with Zucchini Sauce

8 tablespoon unsalted butter
2 lb zucchini, trimmed and chopped
4 large onions (1 lb)
1 tablespoon kosher salt
1 cup parsley

Melt butter in large saute pan. Add zucchini, onions, and salt and saute over medium heat about 10 minutes or until vegetables are very soft. Set aside and cool for 15 minutes. In blender puree the vegetables with the parsley. Toss pasts with sauce, adding a little of the pasta water if sauce is too thick. 